limitedClone

public Supplier limitedClone()
A clone method designed to ONLY be used before any of the coordination fit data has been added. So it clones the organisation added + the data regarding how well it evaluates vs the specified criteria. It purposefully doesn't do the coordination fit stuff which I'm assuming not to have been initialised when this is used.
